name: Parabolic Dreams
description: J-KIND, a techno and tech-house DJ from San Francisco is associated with the Burning Man group Airpusher Collective and is known for his dynamic and explosive sets, pioneering many underground after-parties and big club events, from the Bay to the Burning Man desert, to Ibiza and beyond. Parabolic Dreams is an incredible melodic journey through a positive energy field - a raspy growling synth underlays an incredibly catchy melody, forming a unique blend of uplifting sounds guaranteed to bring your spirits up!
